c: 57
v: 13
t: "ywm yaqul almunafiqun walmunafiqat liladhin amnu, wahum ealaa alsrat: antzrwna nstdy min nwrkm, fataqul lahum almlaykt: arjieuu wara'akum fatlbu nwrana (skhryt mnhm), fafusil baynahum bisur lah bab, batinuh mimaa yali almuminin fih alrhmt, wazahiruh mimaa yali almunafiqin min jihatih aledhab"